======================================================================
Misc.
----------------------------------------------------------------------

- Google Mock
    This library uses the Google Mock library for testing purepose only,
    so you don't have to include the NOTICE of it.

- The SoX Resampler library
    This library uses the soxr library for example app or benchmarking purpose only,
    so you don't have to include the NOTICE of it.

- libfresample library
    This library uses the libfresample library for example app or benchmarking purpose only, 
    so you don't have to include the NOTICE of it.

- android-ndk-profiler
    This library uses the soxr library for example app or benchmarking purpose only,
    so you don't have to include the NOTICE of it.
